BTTTriggers.BTTPredefinedActionName: Run Apple Script in background (enter directly as text)
BTTTriggers.BTTInlineAppleScript: tell application "Google Chrome"	set windows_list to every window	repeat with w in windows_list		set tabs_list to every tab in w		repeat with t in tabs_list			if URL of t starts with "https://hangouts.google.com/hangouts/_/" then				tell application "Google Chrome"					execute t javascript "var el = document.querySelector('.ha-w-P-y-Xi-f').parentNode;el.dispatchEvent(new MouseEvent('mousedown'));el.dispatchEvent(new MouseEvent('mouseup'));el.dispatchEvent(new MouseEvent('mouseout'));"				end tell			end if		end repeat	end repeatend tell

BTTTriggerConfig.BTTTouchBarAppleScriptString: tell application "Google Chrome"	set windows_list to every window	repeat with w in windows_list		set tabs_list to every tab in w		repeat with t in tabs_list			if URL of t starts with "https://hangouts.google.com/hangouts/_/" then				tell application "Google Chrome"					set get_status to execute t javascript "var el = document.querySelector('[aria-label=\"Unmute microphone\"]'); if(el) { true } else { var el = document.querySelector('[aria-label=\"Mute microphone\"]'); if(el){ false } else { null } } "					set status to ((get_status) as string)					if (status is "true") then						return "Unmute"					else if (status is "false") then						return "Mute"					else						return ""					end if				end tell			end if		end repeat	end repeatend tellreturn ""

BTTTriggerConfig.BTTTouchBarAppleScriptString: tell application "Google Chrome"	set windows_list to every window	repeat with w in windows_list		set tabs_list to every tab in w		repeat with t in tabs_list			if URL of t starts with "https://hangouts.google.com/hangouts/_/" then				tell application "Google Chrome"					set get_status to execute t javascript "var el = document.querySelector('[aria-label=\"Turn camera off\"]'); if(el) { true } else { var el = document.querySelector('[aria-label=\"Turn camera on\"]'); if(el) { false } else { null } } "					set status to ((get_status) as string)					if (status is "true") then						return "Turn camera off"					else if (status is "false") then						return "Turn camera on"					else						return ""					end if				end tell			end if		end repeat	end repeatend tellreturn ""
